      +0.73%
    </span></a> <!----></span></span> Labs to build out zkWASM, a zero-knowledge prover for WebAssembly blockchains. The collaboration aims to make zkWASM available for those working with the Polygon Chain Development Kit, a software development kit for building Ethereum compatible networks. The move makes Near Foundation a key contributor to Polygon CDK and improves trustless interoperability between Near, Ethereum and the broader web3 ecosystem, the company said in a </span><a href="https://www.prnewswire.com/news-releases/near-foundation-and-polygon-labs-join-forces-to-build-zero-knowledge-solution-for-wasm-chains-301978354.html" data-v-f87c67ca="">statement</a>.&nbsp;
